Document: loggerhead
Title: Loggerhead: A web viewer for bzr/git branches
Abstract: Loggerhead is a web viewer for projects in Breezy.
 It can be used to navigate a branch history, annotate files,
 view patches, perform searches, etc.
Section: Project Management

Format: HTML
Index: /usr/share/doc/loggerhead/html/index.html
Files: /usr/share/doc/loggerhead/html/*.html
